    {"parameters":{"content":"Purpose\n\nThis workflow automates the applicant screening process by analyzing uploaded transcripts, evaluating academic qualifications against the admission criteria, and managing applicant status. It reduces manual evaluation time and ensures a consistent and objective admission process.","height":288,"width":304},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-240,80],"typeVersion":1,"id":"2710df2b-958e-4840-ba35-5d7ad66f13bd","name":"Sticky Note"},
    {"parameters":{"content":"Workflow Steps:\n1. Google Sheets Trigger\nDetects new or updated applicant records in Google Sheets.\n\n2. Download File\nDownloads the applicant's uploaded transcript (PDF) from Google Drive.\n\n3. Extract Transcript PDF\nExtracts text and academic information from the transcript.","height":400,"width":608,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[112,208],"typeVersion":1,"id":"291f347b-b46b-4070-b3e6-81d78992569d","name":"Sticky Note1"},
    {"parameters":{"content":"Workflow Requirements:\n\n4. Analyze Academic Record\nThe AI model analyzes the transcript, computes academic performance (e.g., GWA), and generates structured output using the Output Parser.\n\n5. Check Admission Workflow Requirements:\nValidates whether the applicant meets the predefined admission requirements based on the extracted academic data.","height":592,"width":752,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[736,160],"typeVersion":1,"id":"2f53916e-4151-405c-8010-5dcc1fdc83aa","name":"Sticky Note2"},
    {"parameters":{"content":"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n6. Update Applicant Record\nSaves or updates the evaluation results in the admissions Google Sheet.\n\n7. Decision Node – Check if Qualified\nDetermines whether the applicant qualifies for admission based on the evaluation results.","height":608,"width":448,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[1520,144],"typeVersion":1,"id":"b78bd361-951e-4f22-b268-1d5d4824efb9","name":"Sticky Note3"},
    {"parameters":{"content":"If Qualified\n1. Schedule an interview using Google Calendar.\n2. Update the applicant record with the interview details.\n3. Automatically send an interview invitation via Gmail.","height":352,"width":720,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[1984,128],"typeVersion":1,"id":"6e165fd6-109e-4b48-928e-7f83990a6c20","name":"Sticky Note4"},
    {"parameters":{"content":"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nIf Not Qualified\n1. Automatically send a rejection letter via Gmail.\n2. Record the applicant's evaluation status in the admissions sheet.","height":352,"width":416},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[1984,480],"typeVersion":1,"id":"da90bf6c-399d-4e3c-8e02-397cd65bbc71","name":"Sticky Note5"}
